&lt;p&gt;ShipStation Global has an opening for a Help Desk Administrator who will be the front-facing member of the IT department and interact with end-users via email, phone, or in person.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The Help Desk Administrator will support Macs, PCs, printers, and related equipment. Tasks include end user support, license tracking, audits, low-level systems management, and routine maintenance tasks.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(17, 0, 58); font-weight: bold; padding-top: 8px; padding-right: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; border: 3px solid rgb(92, 80, 255); margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 8px; text-align: center; font-size: 12px; border-radius: 8px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;What will you be doing?&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
