&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide helpdesk support to resolve problems to the end user’s satisfaction.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Monitor and respond quickly to the help desk ticket queue.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Onboarding of new users.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Install, test and configure new workstations, equipment, and software.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Assist in maintaining an accurate inventory of all equipment and license assignments.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work in a team and effectively interact with others.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Escalate issues to senior staff as necessary.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
