&lt;p&gt;We are looking for a highly analytical, detail-oriented, and hands-on &lt;strong&gt;Carrier Operations Manager/Analyst&lt;/strong&gt; to join our European Carrier Partnerships team for a maternity cover.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;During our busiest time of the year - Peak Season and Q1 contract renewals - you will act as the operational backbone for our team. While our Senior Managers focus on high-level commercial negotiations and carrier strategy, you will take ownership of the critical backend operations that keep our Resell carrier services running smoothly across Europe. You will sit at the intersection of carrier pricing, financial cost control, and product configuration, ensuring that our negotiated rates are accurately implemented and our margins are protected.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;color: #11003a; font-weight: bold; padding: 8px; border: 3px solid #5C50FF; margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 8px; text-align: center; font-size: 12px; border-radius: 8px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;What will you be doing?&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt; Rate Card &amp;amp; Commercial Operations (Core Focus)&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Take ownership of the base rate cards (&quot;buy rates&quot;) for our Resell carriers across the EU.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Translate newly signed carrier contracts and addendums into operational Excel files, ready for upload into Auctane’s backend systems.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Execute highly time-sensitive rate adjustments, heavily focusing on monthly fuel surcharge updates and complex Peak Season surcharges.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ensure the internal Pricing Team is fed accurate, real-time base costs so they can correctly configure final markups and retail pricing.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&l

